            <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left text-[0.6875rem] font-medium text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-zinc-800">Status</th>
            <th class="px-3 py-2 text-right text-[0.6875rem] font-medium text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-zinc-800">Attempts</th>
